Package: ineqTrees
Title: Tree-Based Decomposition of Health Inequality
Version: 0.0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Moses", "Mburu", , "mmburu20@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7281-583X"))
Description: Provides tools for analysing socioeconomic inequality in
    health outcomes with tree-based models. The package supports
    inequality-aware recursive partitioning, weighted ranking and
    concentration-index utilities, subgroup interpretation, and SHAP-based
    decomposition of fitted outcomes into determinant contributions.
